BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 131.52 600 Td (Chapter 1: What is AI?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Artificial Intelligence, or AI, is simply a computer program that can) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (learn and make decisions, much like how you learn from experience.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Think of it as a very smart assistant that gets better over time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (AI is not a robot or a person - it is software running on computers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (You already use AI every day without knowing it. When your email) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (filters spam, that is AI working. When your phone suggests words) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (as you type, that is AI too. It spots patterns and makes guesses.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (AI learns from huge amounts of information, called data. The more) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (data it processes, the better it gets at its job. It is like how you) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (get better at cooking the more recipes you try.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (The good news: you do not need to be technical to benefit from AI.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (This book will show you exactly how to use it in plain English.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
