BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Banks use AI to detect fraud on your credit card automatically.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (The weather app on your phone uses AI to make better predictions.) Tj ET

