BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 81.6 600 Td (Chapter 4: ChatGPT Explained Simply) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (ChatGPT is an AI tool made by a company called OpenAI.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (It is like having a conversation with a very knowledgeable assistant.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (You type a question or request, and it types back an answer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (It was trained by reading billions of pages of text from books and websites.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (This is why it can discuss almost any topic in a helpful way.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (ChatGPT does not search the internet - it uses what it already learned.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Think of it like asking a friend who has read every book in the library.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (It can write emails, explain things simply, give advice, and more.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (It is free to use at chat.openai.com with a basic account.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (You do not need to download anything - it works in your web browser.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (ChatGPT is not perfect. It can sometimes give wrong information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Always double-check important facts, especially about health or money.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 296 Td (Despite its limits, it is an incredibly useful tool for everyday tasks.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
