BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 54.72 600 Td (Chapter 5: How to Use ChatGPT Step by Step) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Step 1: Open your web browser \(Chrome, Safari, or Firefox\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Step 2: Go to chat.openai.com and click Sign Up for a free account.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Step 3: Enter your email and create a password, then verify your email.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Step 4: Once logged in, you will see a text box at the bottom.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Step 5: Type your question or request in plain English and press Enter.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (The key to good results is being specific with your requests.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Instead of asking 'tell me about cooking', try 'give me a simple) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (recipe for chicken soup that takes less than 30 minutes'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (You can ask follow-up questions - ChatGPT remembers the conversation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (If you do not like an answer, say 'try again' or 'explain it simpler'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (You can start a new conversation anytime by clicking New Chat.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Practice makes perfect - the more you use it, the easier it gets.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
