BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 47.04000000000002 600 Td (Chapter 6: AI & Your Job - Should You Worry?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Many people worry that AI will take their jobs. Let us look at facts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (AI is best at repetitive tasks: data entry, sorting, basic analysis.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Jobs that require human touch, creativity, and empathy are safer.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Healthcare workers, teachers, counselors, and tradespeople are in demand.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (AI is more likely to change jobs than eliminate them completely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Think of how ATMs changed banking but did not eliminate all tellers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (The best approach is to learn how to work alongside AI tools.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (People who use AI to do their jobs better will be most successful.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (If you are retired or near retirement, AI is more of a helper than threat.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (It can help you manage finances, stay healthy, and stay connected.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (For those still working, learning basic AI tools is a smart investment.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Remember: AI is a tool, like a calculator. It helps humans do more.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
