q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (AI is making healthcare better and more accessible for everyone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Doctors use AI to read X-rays and catch diseases earlier.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (AI can spot patterns in medical images that humans might miss.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Some apps use AI to check symptoms before you visit the doctor.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (AI helps pharmacies check for dangerous drug interactions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Wearable devices like Apple Watch use AI to monitor heart rhythms.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (AI chatbots can answer basic health questions at any time of day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Researchers use AI to develop new medicines faster than before.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (AI helps hospitals schedule appointments and reduce wait times.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Important: AI should support your doctor, not replace them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Always consult a real doctor for serious health concerns.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (AI health tools work best as a first step, not a final answer.) Tj ET

