BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 58.56 600 Td (Chapter 9: Is AI Safe? Privacy & Security) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (AI safety is a valid concern. Here is what you should know.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (AI tools collect data about you to improve their services.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Be careful what personal information you share with AI chatbots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Never give AI tools your passwords, Social Security number, or PINs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Most reputable AI companies have privacy policies - read them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Your conversations with ChatGPT may be used to improve the system.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (You can usually opt out of data sharing in the settings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (AI can be used by scammers to write convincing fake emails.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Be extra cautious of emails or calls that seem too good to be true.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (The same rules apply: never click suspicious links or share personal info.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Overall, AI is safe to use if you follow basic internet safety rules.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Think of AI like any tool - it is safe when used responsibly.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
