BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (AI can summarize long articles or emails in seconds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (It can draft replies to messages so you just need to review and send.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (AI calendar tools can schedule meetings and set reminders for you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Voice assistants can set timers, make calls, and send texts hands-free.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (AI can help you organize photos by automatically tagging faces and places.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Meal planning AI tools can create weekly menus based on your preferences.) Tj ET
