BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (The average person can save 1-2 hours daily using AI tools effectively.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start with one AI tool and add more as you get comfortable.) Tj ET

