BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 77.75999999999999 600 Td (Chapter 13: Common AI Myths Debunked) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Myth 1: AI will become conscious and take over the world.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Reality: Current AI has no consciousness or desires. It is just math.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Myth 2: AI is always right and you can trust everything it says.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Reality: AI makes mistakes and can give outdated or wrong information.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Myth 3: AI will replace all human jobs within a few years.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Reality: AI changes jobs more than it eliminates them completely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Myth 4: You need to be a computer expert to use AI.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Reality: Modern AI tools are designed to be used by everyday people.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Myth 5: AI is too expensive for regular people to use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Reality: Many powerful AI tools are completely free to use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Myth 6: AI can read your mind or know everything about you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Reality: AI only knows what data it has been given or trained on.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 296 Td (Do not let myths stop you from exploring these helpful tools.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
