BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Use AI to help write fun stories featuring your grandchildren as characters.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (AI can suggest age-appropriate activities for grandkids of any age.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Video call AI features can add fun filters that kids love.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (AI can help you learn the latest games and trends kids enjoy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Use AI to create personalized quizzes or scavenger hunts for visits.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (AI translation tools help if grandchildren speak a different language.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (AI can help you find and order perfect gifts based on their interests.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Use AI to plan fun outings by asking for local activity suggestions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (AI can help you stay current on topics so you can relate to them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (You can use AI to create photo books and memory collections easily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Being tech-savvy makes you an even more amazing grandparent.) Tj ET

