BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 62.400000000000006 600 Td (Chapter 15: Smart Home Devices Explained) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Smart home devices are gadgets that connect to the internet and respond to you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (The most popular are Amazon Echo \(Alexa\) and Google Nest \(Google Assistant\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (These devices sit in your home and listen for a wake word like 'Alexa'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (You can ask them to play music, set timers, read news, and answer questions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Smart lights can be controlled by voice - say 'turn off the lights'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Smart thermostats learn your schedule and save money on heating and cooling.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Smart doorbells let you see who is at your door from your phone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Smart plugs let you turn any device on or off with your voice.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (These devices are easy to set up - usually just plug in and connect to WiFi.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Privacy tip: you can mute the microphone when not using voice features.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Smart home devices can make daily life easier, especially as we age.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start with one device and add more as you see how helpful they are.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
