BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 85.44 600 Td (Chapter 16: Voice Assistants Guide) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Voice assistants let you control your phone and devices just by talking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (The main ones are Siri \(Apple\), Alexa \(Amazon\), and Google Assistant.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (To use Siri, say 'Hey Siri' or press and hold the side button on iPhone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (To use Alexa, say 'Alexa' followed by your request.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (To use Google Assistant, say 'Hey Google' or 'OK Google'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (You can ask them to make phone calls: 'Call my daughter'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (They can send texts: 'Send a message to John saying I will be late'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (They set reminders: 'Remind me to take my medicine at 8 PM'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (They play music: 'Play relaxing jazz music' or 'Play Frank Sinatra'.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (They answer questions: 'What is the weather tomorrow?') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (They can even tell jokes or play trivia games to pass the time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Speak naturally and clearly - you do not need special commands.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
