BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 100.80000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 17: AI & Your Finances) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (AI is changing how we manage money, mostly for the better.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Banks use AI to detect fraudulent transactions on your accounts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (If someone steals your card info, AI often catches it before you do.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Budgeting apps like Mint use AI to categorize your spending automatically.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (AI can analyze your bills and suggest where you could save money.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Robo-advisors use AI to manage investments at lower costs than human advisors.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (AI tools can help you compare insurance rates and find better deals.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Tax preparation software uses AI to find deductions you might miss.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Be cautious: never give AI tools direct access to your bank accounts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Use AI financial tools for information and planning, not direct control.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (AI cannot predict the stock market - be wary of anyone who claims this.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (The best approach: use AI for financial education and organization.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
