BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 43.20000000000002 600 Td (Chapter 18: Future of AI \(Simple Predictions\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (AI will continue to get better and more useful in the coming years.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Healthcare AI will help diagnose diseases earlier and more accurately.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Self-driving cars will become more common but it will take many years.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (AI assistants will become more conversational and helpful over time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Education will be personalized - AI tutors that adapt to each student.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Translation will improve so language barriers nearly disappear.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (AI will help scientists solve big problems like climate change.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (More jobs will involve working alongside AI as a helpful partner.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (AI tools will become simpler and easier for everyone to use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Privacy protections and AI regulations will continue to develop.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (The pace of change may feel fast but you can learn at your own speed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (The most important thing is to stay curious and keep learning.) Tj ET

endstream
